trans-unit.source: Provides a design-time editor in a design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvsext](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeNodeCollection"></xref> object.
Initiates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.TreeNodeCollectionEditor"></xref> class.
Edits the specified object's value using the editor style indicated by the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditor.GetEditStyle*> method.
An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
An <xref:System.IServiceProvider> that this editor can use to obtain services.
The new value of the object.
If the value of the object has not changed, this should return the same object it was passed.
Retrieves the edit style that is used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.TreeNodeCollectionEditor.EditValue*> method.
An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.

A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref> value that indicates the style of editor used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.TreeNodeCollectionEditor.EditValue*> method. If the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditor"></xref> does not support this method, then <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditor.GetEditStyle*> will return <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle"></xref>.
